text: Krishna Lal Maharjan (born December 15, 1954) is a Nepalese politician who serves as the Member Of The House Of Representatives (Nepal). He was elected from Lalitpur-2, Province No. 3. He is a member of the Communist Party of Nepal (Unified Socialist). ==References== Category:1954 births Category:Living people Category:Nepalese politicians
title: Krishna Lal Maharjan
